{"tid":2096000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"史墨客：黨安法或令香港難以維持金融地位  白宮正檢視其他措施回應","createTime":"2020-07-06T01:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T01:35:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"00f662084b2f6e6dddbe618a7b6505cacf47236f","tid":2096000,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"史墨客：港區國安法或令香港難以維持金融地位 <br />\n發佈時間 2020-07-06 08:41<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港總領事史墨客在一個電台節目表示，相當憂慮港區國安法實施，美國在香港有龐大的社群，關注知識產權的保障及資訊流動等會否受到港區國安法影響，如果香港的成功根基，包括開放、透明及言論自由受損，香港難以維持原有的金融地位。他指，白宮正檢視其他措施，以回應北京今次立法。 史墨客認為，港區國安法反映中央的不安，亦令香港的高度自治受損，擔心長遠而言香港難以維持競爭力，又認為中央管治香港的手法，越來越像管治內地其他城市。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345526&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=c61822a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345526</a>"},{"pid":"fb216a0fcb734dc22b25eb0d3632a3d25b89b4af","tid":2096000,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"史墨客 呢個名係點釋岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1211e6dbb48726e2d8cdfc30111119f42342d16b","tid":2096000,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd484cf841ca3edebb0deb0e5d4d1bf6a3537b82","tid":2096000,"uid":9056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"政府：香港既地位係基本法賦予....."},{"pid":"a123d97dec2dc87fa1e7ae89eebb1fe0b153d9fd","tid":2096000,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2